{"tid":1526411,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋需要一班能夠進退自如嘅勇武。","createTime":"2019-09-01T05:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T09:26:31.000Z","uid":216995,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f5cbf10889052051e66fb5b5db91655f76075987","tid":1526411,"uid":216995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:43:36.000Z","msg":"每次睇到勇武比狗狗咬係因為後面一大堆帶豬嘴食花生而造成一個人多嘅錯覺比前線。同埋佢哋太有愛一直想掩護後排導致自己落後。<br />\n<br />\n真正非理非一定見有事就走，但係硬係有啲撚屌上gear 然後乜都唔做，有事就走先塞哂啲位。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我嘅諗法係前線一完成目標或者自己根據形勢走先，唔好理後面啲花生友。<br />\n<br />\n我知咁諗好似有啲仆街，但係你落得場你預咗有被捕嘅結論後果。驚，點解仲要落？有咩事就自己走先，人又唔救彈又唔滅，不如返去睇直播算，唔好阻人走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾時先可以見到全民勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論"},{"pid":"8d298c021c019106ef65430011761bcaeb45a9cd","tid":1526411,"uid":263058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:44:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6a363274356b722d857d9a699cd6756d3b9d43d","tid":1526411,"uid":216995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:44:17.000Z","msg":"自推十連<br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n831"},{"pid":"50e8fb51552ebe3d51690996aca01ee96a27d492","tid":1526411,"uid":216995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:44:29.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811<br />\n831"},{"pid":"2fca7dbd0ebfd722d96743c45f61ace8e89142d2","tid":1526411,"uid":216995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:44:43.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811<br />\n831"},{"pid":"e11c2dd9b6959ddf2c7a4db50e3aaba85104e584","tid":1526411,"uid":216995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:44:55.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811<br />\n831"},{"pid":"8b62623f6babcfacd5c5133918e70c45f31b71ad","tid":1526411,"uid":216995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:45:05.000Z","msg":"721<br />